334
00:18:15,470 --> 00:18:16,700
I've found it for you.

335
00:18:16,700 --> 00:18:17,510
Come here.

336
00:18:22,310 --> 00:18:23,590
The table. Books.

337
00:18:23,960 --> 00:18:25,950
