342
00:18:36,590 --> 00:18:37,390
Very good.

343
00:18:56,550 --> 00:18:57,350
Nice place.

344
00:18:59,930 --> 00:19:00,830
Nice place?

345
00:19:07,670 --> 00:19:08,550
Young Master.

346
00:19:08,920 --> 00:19:11,910
