Honey.

349
00:19:37,590 --> 00:19:39,550
Xiao Qiu told me you wanted to see me.

350
00:19:39,550 --> 00:19:40,150
Darling.

351
00:19:40,150 --> 00:19:41,030
Have a seat.

352
