512
00:29:11,270 --> 00:29:13,120
We'll have a romantic date at dusk,

513
00:29:13,120 --> 00:29:14,950
willows drifting in the breeze.

514
00:29:16,870 --> 00:29:17,790
It's so cringy.

515
00:29:24,390 --> 00:29:26,270
Midnight is an ideal time

516
00:29:26,270 --> 00:29:28,240
for one to commit arson and murder.

517
00:29:30,230 --> 00:29:31,400
What is this?

518
00:29:48,070 --> 00:29:55,070
Half past seven.

519
00:29:56,570 --> 00:29:58,950
[Half past seven at Chang An]

520
00:29:56,990 --> 00:30:03,630
See you at Chang An Bridge. Be there or be square.

521
00:30:05,470 --> 00:30:08,470
Mr. Liu.

522
00:30:11,690 --> 00:30:14,850
[See you at Chang An Bridge at half past seven. Be there or be square. It's up to you to show up or not.]

523
00:30:14,880 --> 00:30:15,860
