528
00:31:05,870 --> 00:31:08,280
Obviously, she trusted me that I wouldn't read it without her permission.

529
00:31:08,280 --> 00:31:10,010
I can't let her down.

530
00:32:05,110 --> 00:32:06,870
Half past seven.

531
00:32:07,030 --> 00:32:09,510
See you at Chang An Bridge. Be there or be square.

532
00:32:09,510 --> 00:32:11,110
It's up to you to show up or not.

533
00:32:11,110 --> 00:32:12,590
Mr. Liu.

534
00:32:19,040 --> 00:32:19,840
Young Master.

535
00:32:21,450 --> 00:32:23,270
Young Madam is urging you to have dinner.

536
00:32:23,270 --> 00:32:25,600
Old Madam has been waiting for a long time.

537
00:32:27,230 --> 00:32:28,360
I'll be right there.

538
00:32:57,950 --> 00:32:59,630
Chen, come and join us.

539
00:33:19,150 --> 00:33:19,990
Zhen

540
00:33:19,990 --> 00:33:21,950
asked the cook to make these delicacies.

541
00:33:21,950 --> 00:33:22,990
Eat more.

542
00:33:23,340 --> 00:33:24,310
Okay, Mother.

543
00:33:55,550 --> 00:33:56,280
Xiao Qiu.

544
00:33:57,010 --> 00:33:59,590
Xiao Dong said he put a letter for me

545
00:33:59,590 --> 00:34:01,070
on my desk.

546
00:34:01,070 --> 00:34:02,310
Can you bring it to me?

547
00:34:02,470 --> 00:34:03,600
Yes, Your Ladyship.

548
00:34:13,320 --> 00:34:13,909
Mother.

549
00:34:14,110 --> 00:34:15,199
I have a bad memory.

550
00:34:15,199 --> 00:34:17,520
I have an appointment with Wu Zhao at the restaurant at 7 p.m.

551
00:34:17,520 --> 00:34:19,179
I can't leave him there alone.

552
00:34:19,840 --> 00:34:21,639
Please go ahead with the dinner.

553
00:34:27,190 --> 00:34:27,870
Zhen.

554
00:34:28,440 --> 00:34:30,550
Do you have an appointment too?

555
00:34:31,190 --> 00:34:32,590
Sit down and eat with me.

556
00:35:08,750 --> 00:35:09,430
Xu Ning.

557
00:35:10,110 --> 00:35:11,690
♫Hands over the sadness♫

558
00:35:10,670 --> 00:35:11,550
Did you wait long?

559
00:35:11,550 --> 00:35:12,390
No, I just arrived.

560
00:35:12,110 --> 00:35:15,980
