564
00:35:26,460 --> 00:35:28,180
♫When will old ones glance back?♫

565
00:35:28,560 --> 00:35:33,020
♫In this worldly dance, parting brings so much bitterness♫

566
00:35:34,850 --> 00:35:36,550
♫We can't be together♫

567
00:35:36,880 --> 00:35:39,470
♫Yearning floods like a river♫

568
00:35:37,030 --> 00:35:37,790
Liu Rong.

569
00:35:37,790 --> 00:35:38,830
Why are you so excited?

570
00:35:38,830 --> 00:35:39,950
Look at you.

571
00:35:39,950 --> 00:35:41,350
Can you be more reserved?

572
00:35:41,380 --> 00:35:42,950
♫Who's right and who's wrong?♫

573
00:35:43,520 --> 00:35:45,470
♫There's no right or wrong in this world♫

574
00:35:43,810 --> 00:35:44,990
He went out.

575
00:35:45,640 --> 00:35:47,080
Why am I so happy?

576
00:35:45,680 --> 00:35:49,510
♫We're strangers, but we're on different sides♫

577
00:35:49,780 --> 00:35:51,260
♫Amidst the tumult of life's fireworks♫

578
00:35:51,880 --> 00:35:56,260
♫I'll land on your heart even if I have to keep circling♫

579
00:35:52,110 --> 00:35:53,350
He went out!

